headline: Coinbase earnings, jobless claims, mortgage rates: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime's Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview the biggest economic data and market stories to come on Thursday, May 8, including earnings out from Coinbase Global (COIN), ConocoPhillips (COP), and Anheuser-Busch Inbev (BUD), as well as weekly updates on initial jobless claims and US mortgage rates. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
